    "created_at": "2013-08-13T07:16:35Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-08-13T16:04:03Z",
    "body": "Your request means:\n1. The menu item's state and attributes should be able to be changed dynamically without recreating the whole menu.\n2. Provide a way in `Menu.buildFromTemplate` API to add custom fields to menu items.\n\nis it right?\n\nThe menu API was implemented by reusing Chromium's ui library, which is designed for static menus, e.g. there is no way to change menu items without recreating the whole menu with this library. I'll get rid of Chromium's menu library and write the menu API from scratch.\n"
  },
